We Are Teaching
19 Modern Wealth Creation Methods

Freelancing: Make money selling your skills. You’ll learn how to get paid a premium price to complete simple tasks. Then we’ll teach you the most effective methods to build a list of loyal clients.

Copywriting: Master the art of selling with words. We will teach you how to write persuasive advertisements, emails, tweets.

E-Commerce: Industry experts will train you to find winning products, create the perfect store, and generate free or paid traffic for your website or marketplace.

Business & Finance: We will provide you with training to be fully in control of your operations, hiring, and finances. Then we will provide you with detailed training on how to scale your business to achieve seven-figure revenues.

Mindset: Our instructors will teach you the mental strategies that have contributed to their own success, helping you to develop a more successful mindset. To achieve financial success, it is important to adopt a millionaire mindset.

Artificial Intelligence: Our business models all incorporate the latest AI tools that are available on the market. We will provide you with training on how to utilize AI to gain a competitive advantage in your business.

Stock Analysis: Multiply your capital through the stock market. We will teach you how to find opportunities in traditional markets and how to capitalize off them.

Crypto: Profit from the world’s highest-performing assets. We will help you identify which style of investing is best suited to your personality, financial status, and investing time horizon.

Flipping: It's a short term investment strategy where the goal is to buy low and sell high. We will teach you which categories and items are most profitable for flipping. You can start flipping with as little as $5.

Social Media Marketing: We will help you to build brand awareness, loyalty, trust. We will teach you how to rapidly grow your social media accounts on platforms such as Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, Twitter...

Health & Fitness: Tristan and Andrew Tate's personal trainer will teach you everything you need to know about fitness and health. You will have access to Nutrition Plans, Workout Plans, Short Videos With Physical Exercises.

New Skills (not mentioned here): Now, with our own payment processors, servers, and banks, we can share previously undisclosed methods of wealth creation that were not available in Hustler's University 2.0 & HU 3.0.
